Athena Capital | About



























 




















COMMITTED TO THE CLIENT EXPERIENCE
A track record of performance and service
Founded in 1993 and based in Lincoln, Massachusetts, we are a privately owned, independent Registered Investment Advisor (RIA). We earn clients' trust by understanding and meeting their investment objectives to deliver an exceptional experience.






High Net Worth
Foundations & Endowments
Impact Investing














