Athena Capital Advisors LLC Company Profile

   Athena Capital Advisors hopes to remove the headaches involved with financial planning. Athena Capital Advisors specializes in providing investment services for wealthy families and institutions, offering portfolio advisory and research services. The company's institutional clients include hedge funds, private equity funds, and real estate firms. The firm was established in 1993 by Lisette Cooper, Athena's president.
  
